file_path = 'train-00.txt'
reader = DisCoCircReader()
# Open the file using a context manager
with open(file_path, 'r') as file:
    # Iterate through each line in the file
    for i, line in enumerate(file):
        try:
            print(f' sample -> {i}, \n {line.strip()}')
            diagram = reader.text2circuit(line.strip())
            diagram.draw(figsize=(12, 8), foliated=False, draw_type_labels=False, color_boxes=False, color_wire=True)
        except Exception as e:
            # Skip lines that cause exceptions and print an error message
            print(f"Skipping line {i + 1} due to an error: {e}")
